":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's only natural."},{"chara":[{"id":230101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It would be a waste of time@to take the exact same actions."},{"chara":[{"id":230101,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, seeking information from outside@of town was the obvious next step."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That makes sense..."},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200901,"motion":200,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]With each loop, I just felt lucky that I got to@rent different movies with the same money!"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200901}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200901}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-10","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...Maybe that was a bit too lackadaisical@on my part?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":230101,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's very you, Mabayu."},{"bgmFadeOut":4000,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Heh heh..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-13"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":230101}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200901,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Tell me, Miss Akemi..."},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime06","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]How are you able to lay your life@on the line to fight Witches?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":230101,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's all for Madoka."},{"chara":[{"id":230101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Madoka was the one who changed me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Changed you...?"},{"chara":[{"id":230101,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I was cowardly, always protected@by others. Truly useless."},{"chara":[{"id":230101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-20"},{"id":200901,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But...despite that, Madoka fought@against Witches to help me..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":230101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-21"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...and she died."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":230101,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's why I want to protect Madoka."},{"chara":[{"id":230101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Instead of her protecting me,@I want to be the one protecting her."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":230101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-24"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That was my wish."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":230101,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104210/vo_full_911105-010-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So until I manage to see this through@and save Madoka, I won't give up."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
